data.description: Charming cottage meets convenient living. This classic 3 bedroom/2.5 bathroom home sits on nearly an acre lot in Oconee County's HOA-free Oak Pointe neighborhood. It also comes with a finished apartment area over the garage with a separate entrance, and a second full kitchenette,  4th bedroom, 3rd full bath and another living area - perfect for a teen or in-law suite, rental or just additional bedroom and flex spaces.  Brand new roof on the main home and fresh exterior paint make this an exceptional opportunity near all Watkinsville has to offer!
